{"tid":1452721,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警司協會主席陳民德：嚴重傷人罪可被判終身監禁","createTime":"2019-08-12T02:10:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T02:21:10.000Z","uid":139475,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e1a30bc4b5732e6a1b5e6a4e60e3932db6d020d5","tid":1452721,"uid":139475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:10:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1151834&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1151834%26csid%3D261_341&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkUYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=07df5a0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1151834&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n警司協會主席陳民德指，用汽油彈襲擊警察是極端暴力行為，是絕對不能接受的嚴重違法罪行，更形容是恐怖主義行為，<span style=\"color: red;\">根據法例，嚴重傷人罪可被判終身監禁。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咁整盲女仔隻眼單野又點計？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ecf3a062e1db2b5862b3fe041ba38c2df91c7f0","tid":1452721,"uid":134323,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:12:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">汽油彈係警察自己扔</span></span>"},{"pid":"0594ca46d3c867e5eaf032a82a8568922775f050","tid":1452721,"uid":120715,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:14:09.000Z","msg":"咪判囉<br />\n反正係黑警假扮示威者擲汽油彈"},{"pid":"9264f4724bf2e03d73bc55ad887bea1420ac172c","tid":1452721,"uid":166616,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:15:22.000Z","msg":"自己掟自己  仲拉埋自己 一條龍服務 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d49432f636f67c96f8b0ff1943eac86fa252821a","tid":1452721,"uid":139475,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9264f4724bf2e03d73bc55ad887bea1420ac172c","tid":1452721,"uid":166616,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:15:2